de: Amendment No. 1 to Administration Agreement between the Government of the Swiss Confederation and the International Development Association regarding the Nepal Public Financial Management Support Multi-Donor Trust Fund (Trust Fund No. TF071617)  - 19-04-2017 - Abkommen zwischen der Schweiz, vertreten durch das SECO, und IDA betreffend den Multi-Geber Treuhandfonds zur Stärkung des öffentlichen Finanzwesens in Nepal
en: Amendment No. 1 to Administration Agreement between the Government of the Swiss Confederation and the International Development Association regarding the Nepal Public Financial Management Support Multi-Donor Trust Fund (Trust Fund No. TF071617) - 19-04-2017 - Trust Fund Administration Agreement between the Government of the Swiss Confederation and the International Development Association (IDA) concerning the Nepal Public Financial Management Support Multi-Donor Trust Fund (No. TF 071617)
fr: Amendment No. 1 to Administration Agreement between the Government of the Swiss Confederation and the International Development Association regarding the Nepal Public Financial Management Support Multi-Donor Trust Fund (Trust Fund No. TF071617) - 19-04-2017 - Accord entre la Suisse, représentée par SECO, et IDA concernant le fond fiduciaire pour le renforcement de la gestion des finances publiques au Népal
